title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
OB: If you export a directory (project) and place the exported jar in the same directory (project), you will get an out of sync message when you overwrite the exported jarfile the 2nd time.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself.
SR:
Follow these steps to reproduce: 
1. Export a directory (project) 
2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project) 
3. Overwrite the exported jarfile for the second time
